name: vue-router-storage
description: A vue router storage solution. -If your vue application needs to jump to a third party page, and then jump back, want to restore to the original history and continue to operate, the use of this plug-in is the best solution.如果你的vue应用需要跳转到第三方页面，再跳转回来时，想恢复到原来的历史记录并继续操作，使用本插件是最好的解决方案。
